#: ../../language/error_codes/E4055.md:1
msgid "E4055"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4055.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `field_duplicate`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4055.md:5
msgid ""
"Field is already declared. Within one struct declaration, each field name"
" must be unique because field access, construction, and update syntax all"
" identify a field by name."
msgstr ""
"字段已被声明。在同一个结构体声明中，每个字段名都必须唯一，因为字段访问、构造和更新语法都会通过名称来识别字段。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4055.md:9
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4055.md:11
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"struct A {\n"
"  a : Int\n"
"  a : Double\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4055.md:15
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4055.md:17
msgid "Rename the field to a different name."
msgstr "请将字段重命名为其他名称。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4055.md:19
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"priv struct A {\n"
"  a : Int\n"
"  b : Double\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let value : A = { a: 1, b: 2.0 }\n"
"  inspect(value.a, content=\"1\")\n"
"  inspect(value.b, content=\"2\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
